   292→    /**
   293→     * @param {string} post - The ID of the Post to comment on
   294→     * @param {string} member - The ID of the Member to comment as
   295→     * @param {string} comment - The HTML content of the Comment
   296→     * @param {any} options
   297→     * @param {Date} [createdAt] - Optional custom created_at timestamp
